      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "data team will drop csv file on s3\nour worker need to download s3 file \nand save to database. and if save file\nto database success send email to \ndata team and our team. and csv field data\nmust valid by business rule.\n\n\n\n- how we can automate test test?.\n    - unit test?\n    - integration test?\n    - e2e test?",
